Package: choroplethr
Title: Simplify the Creation of Choropleth Maps in R
Description: Choropleths are thematic maps where geographic regions,
        such as states, are colored according to some metric, such as
        the number of people who live in that state. This package
        simplifies this process by 1. Providing ready-made functions
        for creating choropleths of common maps. 2. Providing data and
        API connections to interesting data sources for making
        choropleths. 3. Providing a framework for creating choropleths
        from arbitrary shapefiles. 4. Overlaying those maps over
        reference maps from Google Maps.
